rows.label: tlk70000053_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Hi everyone, and welcome to the
militia camp!

rows.label: tlk70000053_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Here people from all different countries
and social standings live together under
one roof! Figuratively. We live in tents.

rows.label: tlk70000053_01_msg0003
rows.name:
It was all Adel-sama's idea! At first
we were separated based on homeland,
but that didn't work out very well.

rows.label: tlk70000053_01_msg0004
rows.name:
There were some rough patches when
we adopted Adel-sama's plan, but he
helped us resolve our differences.

rows.label: tlk70000053_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Now we care more about who snores
at night than who's from where!

rows.label: tlk70000053_01_msg0006
rows.name:
I'm sure Adel-sama knew we'd get
along like this. I really admire him for
being so forward-thinking.
